Class Matrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • app.Matrix

  • public class Matrix
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the building as a 3D-Matrix for calculating the path between two points in the building. The first dimension of the 3D table represents the floor The last two dimensions represent the coordinates of the cell in the floor Each floor is mapped in a Cartesian system xOy. matrix[k][i][j] represents the cell located at floor k with coordinates (i, j).
